24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-house\"><path d=\"m3 9 9-7 9 7\"></path><path d=\"M9 22V12h6v10\"></path></svg></span>Séance à domicile</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Prix d\'une séance : 70 €</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Je me déplace uniquement sur la Commune de Vernon pour les personnes ne pouvant pas venir au cabinet. Réservations par téléphone au 06 95 64 54 76.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Le paiement peut se faire en espèces ou par chèque à l\'ordre de \"AIMER GUÉRIR\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Je me présenterai à l\'heure convenue au domicile du patient. Durée d’une séance : environ 30 minutes</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Merci de réserver pour le bon déroulement de la séance un espace calme et propre.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\",\"className\":\"appointment-cta__session-media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top appointment-cta__session-media\"><!-- wp:image {\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"appointment-cta__image\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full appointment-cta__image\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/wp-content/themes/my-theme/assets/images/pattern-placeholder-400.svg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":623,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2022-05-07-Nouveau-local-AIMER-GUERIR.avif\" alt=\"Cabinet vu de la rue\" class=\"wp-image-623\"/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Cabinet vu de la rue</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Test','','inherit','closed','closed','','587-revision-v1','','','2026-02-13 16:23:25','2026-02-13 15:23:25','',587,'http://localhost:8080/?p=656',0,'revision','',0),
(657,1,'2026-02-13 16:24:00','2026-02-13 15:24:00','<!-- wp:group {\"metadata\":{\"categories\":[\"my-theme\"],\"patternName\":\"my-theme/appointment-cta\",\"name\":\"Prendre rendez-vous\"},\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"pattern-appointment-cta\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide pattern-appointment-cta\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"appointment-cta__header\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"default\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group appointment-cta__header\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Horaires d\'ouverture du cabinet</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"appointment-cta__schedules\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"default\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group appointment-cta__schedules\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Du lundi au vendredi de 08:30 à 13:00 et de 14:00 à 19:00</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Le samedi de 09:00 à 12:00</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\">\n        <a class=\"wp-block-button__link btn btn--primary btn--icon\" href=\"#\">\n          Réserver une séance\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg>        </a>\n      </div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"appointment-cta__info\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"default\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group appointment-cta__info\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"appointment-cta__card\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"default\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group appointment-cta__card\"><!